Symbol.Script_3D:
! Skewed_window_frame
if gs_frame_mat = gs_frame_mat2 then !!! One body, in case of similar materials in_out_cikl = 1
var_mater = gs_frame_mat var_mater2 = gs_frame_mat
out_thk = 0 part_thk =gs_frame_thk
in_out_mask = 15 in_out_mask2 = 13 if gs_stack_bottom then bot_mask = 8 else bot_mask = 15 else !!!two bodies in_out_cikl = 2
!!! Inner-outer Material Control----------- temp_frame_mat = gs_frame_mat temp_frame_mat2 = gs_frame_mat2 if WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE then gs_frame_mat=temp_frame_mat gs_frame_mat2=temp_frame_mat2 else gs_frame_mat=temp_frame_mat2 gs_frame_mat2=temp_frame_mat endif
var_mater = gs_frame_mat var_mater2 = gs_frame_mat2
if lod3D = 2 then ! Detailed out_thk = gs_frame_thk - gs_rebate_depth part_thk = out_thk else if lod3D = 5 then out_thk = gs_frame_thk/2 else if WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE then out_thk = gs_frame_thk/2 - gs_glass_thk/2 else out_thk = gs_frame_thk/2 + gs_glass_thk/2 endif endif part_thk = out_thk endif
in_out_mask = 11 in_out_mask2 = 9 if gs_stack_bottom then bot_mask = 8 else bot_mask = 11 endif
!! FRAME !!
group "frame"
sect_fill gs_fillFr, gs_penFr_bg, gs_penFr_fg, gs_frame_pen_cont pen gs_frame_pen
! --- Cutting in case of corner window ----------------------------------------- halfA = A / 2 cutLeft = 0 cutRight = 0 if abs(gs_frame_ovhg_left_out - gs_frame_ovhg_left_in) > EPS then addx -halfA - gs_frame_ovhg_left_out rotz 90 cutplane -90 + atn((gs_frame_ovhg_left_out - gs_frame_ovhg_left_in) / gs_frame_thk) del 2 cutLeft = 1 endif if abs(gs_frame_ovhg_right_out - gs_frame_ovhg_right_in) > EPS then addx halfA + gs_frame_ovhg_right_out rotz 90 cutplane 90 - atn((gs_frame_ovhg_right_out - gs_frame_ovhg_right_in) / gs_frame_thk) del 2 cutRight = 1 endif
for ijk = 1 to in_out_cikl material var_mater
if gs_SashText_typ_num = 1 then base cprism_ var_mater2,var_mater,var_mater, 4, part_thk, -a/2+gs_frame_width+simp_mod, frameBottomMiddleY+dysw1, 10, -a/2-leftOvhg, frameBottomMiddleY+dy1, in_out_mask, -a/2-leftOvhg, frameTopMiddleY+dy2, 10, -a/2+gs_frame_width+simp_mod, frameTopMiddleY+dysw2, in_out_mask vert 0, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 0, 1 coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4 body 1
base cprism_ var_mater2,var_mater,var_mater, 4, part_thk, a/2-gs_frame_width-simp_mod, frameBottomMiddleY-dysw2, 10, a/2+rightOvhg, frameBottomMiddleY-dy2, in_out_mask, a/2+rightOvhg, frameTopMiddleY-dy1, 10, a/2-gs_frame_width-simp_mod, frameTopMiddleY-dysw1, in_out_mask vert 0, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 0, 1 coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4 body 1
base cprism_ var_mater2,var_mater,var_mater, 4, part_thk, -a/2-leftOvhg, frameTopMiddleY+dy2, 10, -a/2+gs_frame_width+simp_mod, frameTopMiddleY+dysw2, in_out_mask, a/2-gs_frame_width-simp_mod, frameTopMiddleY-dysw1, 10, a/2+rightOvhg, frameTopMiddleY-dy1, in_out_mask vert 0, 0, 0 vert cos(topAngle), -sin(topAngle), 0 vert sin(topAngle), cos(topAngle), 0 vert 0, 0, 1 coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4 body 1
base cprism_ var_mater2,var_mater,var_mater, 4, part_thk, a/2+rightOvhg, frameBottomMiddleY-dy2, 10, a/2-gs_frame_width-simp_mod, frameBottomMiddleY-dysw2, in_out_mask, -a/2+gs_frame_width+simp_mod, frameBottomMiddleY+dysw1, 10, -a/2-leftOvhg, frameBottomMiddleY+dy1, bot_mask vert 0, 0, 0 vert cos(topAngle), -sin(topAngle), 0 vert sin(topAngle), cos(topAngle), 0 vert 0, 0, 1 coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4 body 1 endif
if gs_SashText_typ_num = 2 then base cprism_ var_mater2,var_mater,var_mater, 4, part_thk, -a/2+gs_frame_width+simp_mod, frameBottomMiddleY+dysw1, 10, -a/2-leftOvhg, frameBottomMiddleY+dysw1, in_out_mask-2, -a/2-leftOvhg, frameTopMiddleY+dysw2, 8, -a/2+gs_frame_width+simp_mod, frameTopMiddleY+dysw2, in_out_mask vert 0, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 0, 1 coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4 body 1
base cprism_ var_mater2,var_mater,var_mater, 4, part_thk, a/2-gs_frame_width-simp_mod, frameBottomMiddleY-dysw2, 8, a/2+rightOvhg, frameBottomMiddleY-dysw2, in_out_mask-2, a/2+rightOvhg, frameTopMiddleY-dysw1, 8, a/2-gs_frame_width-simp_mod, frameTopMiddleY-dysw1, in_out_mask vert 0, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 0, 1 coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4 body 1
base cprism_ var_mater2,var_mater,var_mater, 6, part_thk, -a/2-leftOvhg, frameTopMiddleY+dy2, in_out_mask, -a/2-leftOvhg, frameTopMiddleY+dysw2, 8, -a/2+gs_frame_width+simp_mod, frameTopMiddleY+dysw2, in_out_mask, a/2-gs_frame_width-simp_mod, frameTopMiddleY-dysw1, 10, a/2+rightOvhg, frameTopMiddleY-dysw1, in_out_mask2, a/2+rightOvhg, frameTopMiddleY-dy1, in_out_mask vert 0, 0, 0 vert cos(topAngle), -sin(topAngle), 0 vert sin(topAngle), cos(topAngle), 0 vert 0, 0, 1 coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4 body 1
base cprism_ var_mater2,var_mater,var_mater, 6, part_thk, a/2+rightOvhg, frameBottomMiddleY-dy2, in_out_mask, a/2+rightOvhg, frameBottomMiddleY-dysw2, 8, a/2-gs_frame_width-simp_mod, frameBottomMiddleY-dysw2, in_out_mask, -a/2+gs_frame_width+simp_mod, frameBottomMiddleY+dysw1, 10, -a/2-leftOvhg, frameBottomMiddleY+dysw1, in_out_mask2, -a/2-leftOvhg, frameBottomMiddleY+dy1, bot_mask vert 0, 0, 0 vert cos(topAngle), -sin(topAngle), 0 vert sin(topAngle), cos(topAngle), 0 vert 0, 0, 1 coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4 body 1 endif
addz part_thk part_thk= gs_frame_thk-out_thk
var_mater = gs_frame_mat2 var_mater2 = gs_frame_mat2
in_out_mask = 14 in_out_mask2 = 12 if gs_stack_bottom then bot_mask = 8 else bot_mask = 14
next ijk del in_out_cikl
if cutLeft then cutend if cutRight then cutend endgroup
! ============================================================================== ! Sash cavities in Frame ! ==============================================================================
group "harcsi" if lod3D = 2 then if GLOB_CONTEXT = 4 | GLOB_CONTEXT = 6 then pen gs_frame_pen_cont else pen gs_frame_pen endif sect_fill gs_fillFr, gs_penFr_bg, gs_penFr_fg, gs_frame_pen_cont
if iSashCutType = SASHCUT_REBATE then addz gs_frame_thk - gs_rebate_depth material gs_frame_mat2 prism_ 5, gs_frame_thk, -a/2+gs_frame_width-gs_rebate_width, frameBottomMiddleY+dyrw1, 15, a/2-gs_frame_width+gs_rebate_width, frameBottomMiddleY-dyrw2, 15, a/2-gs_frame_width+gs_rebate_width, frameTopMiddleY-dyrw1, 15, -a/2+gs_frame_width-gs_rebate_width, frameTopMiddleY+dyrw2, 15, -a/2+gs_frame_width-gs_rebate_width, frameBottomMiddleY+dyrw1, -1 body 1 del 1 endif
if iSashCutType = SASHCUT_MIDDLE then addz gs_frame_thk/2 material gs_frame_mat2 prism_ 5, gs_frame_thk, -a/2+gs_frame_width, frameBottomMiddleY+dyfw1, 15, a/2-gs_frame_width, frameBottomMiddleY-dyfw2, 15, a/2-gs_frame_width, frameTopMiddleY-dyfw1, 15, -a/2+gs_frame_width, frameTopMiddleY+dyfw2, 15, -a/2+gs_frame_width, frameBottomMiddleY+dyfw1, -1 body 1 material gs_frame_mat prism_ 5, -gs_frame_thk, -a/2+gs_frame_width, frameBottomMiddleY+dyfw1, 15, a/2-gs_frame_width, frameBottomMiddleY-dyfw2, 15, a/2-gs_frame_width, frameTopMiddleY-dyfw1, 15, -a/2+gs_frame_width, frameTopMiddleY+dyfw2, 15, -a/2+gs_frame_width, frameBottomMiddleY+dyfw1, -1 body 1 del 1 endif endif endgroup
pen gs_frame_pen sect_fill gs_fillFr, gs_penFr_bg, gs_penFr_fg, gs_frame_pen_cont
if lod3D = 2 then ! Detailed placegroup subgroup("frame","harcsi") else placegroup "frame" endif
end
Symbol.Script_1D:
EPS = 0.0001
! gs_optype_m SASH_FIXED = 1 ! Fixed Glass SASH_FIXED_SCREW = 2 ! Fixed Sash SASH_SIDE_HUNG = 3 ! Side Hung SASH_SIDE_HUNG_M = 4 ! Side Hung Mirrored SASH_TILT_TURN = 5 ! Tilt and Turn SASH_TILT_TURN_M = 6 ! Tilt and Turn Mirrored SASH_BOTTOM_HUNG = 7 ! Bottom Hung SASH_TOP_HUNG = 8 ! Top Hung SASH_HOR_PIVOT = 9 ! Horizontal Pivot Hung SASH_VER_PIVOT = 10 ! Vertical Pivotted SASH_TILT_SLIDE = 11 ! Tilt and Slide SASH_LEFT_SLIDING = 12 ! Left Sliding SASH_RIGHT_SLIDING = 13 ! Right Sliding SASH_UP_SLIDING = 14 ! Sliding Up SASH_DOWN_SLIDING = 15 ! Sliding Down SASH_VER_PIVOT_M = 16 ! Vertical Pivotted Mirrored SASH_FIXED_SLIDE = 17 ! Fixed Sliding Sash SASH_DOUBLE_SIDE_HUNG = 18 ! Double Sash SASH_DOUBLE_TILT_TURN = 19 ! Double Tilt and Turn SASH_DOUBLE_TILT_TURN_M = 20 ! Double Tilt and Turn Mirrored SASH_SLIDING_HOR = 21 ! Sliding SASH_SLIDING_HOR_M = 22 ! Sliding Mirrored SASH_DOUBLE_SLIDING_HOR = 23 ! Double Sliding SASH_DOUBLE_SLIDING_HOR_M = 24 ! Double Sliding Mirrored SASH_SLIDING_VER = 25 ! Single Hung SASH_DOUBLE_SLIDING_VER = 26 ! Double Hung
! iMullionStyle MULLION_NONE = 1 MULLION_HVGRID = 2 MULLION_EDITABLEGRID = 3 MULLION_CUSTOM = 4 MULLION_PRAIRIE = 5 MULLION_DIVIDED = 6
! iSashCutType SASHCUT_NONE = 0 SASHCUT_REBATE = 1 SASHCUT_MIDDLE = 2
!!Angle and coordinate calculation!!
simp_mod = 0 if lod3D = 1 | lod3D = 5 then ! Simple | Chinese if gs_optype_m_01 <> SASH_FIXED then simp_mod = gs_sash_width - gs_rebate_width if gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_HOR_PIVOT |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_VER_PIVOT |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_VER_PIVOT_M |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_SLIDING_HOR |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_SLIDING_HOR_M |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_DOUBLE_SLIDING_HOR |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_DOUBLE_SLIDING_HOR_M |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_SLIDING_VER |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_DOUBLE_SLIDING_VER then simp_mod = gs_sash_width else if gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_SLIDING_HOR |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_SLIDING_HOR_M |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_DOUBLE_SLIDING_HOR |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_DOUBLE_SLIDING_HOR_M |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_SLIDING_VER |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_DOUBLE_SLIDING_VER then simp_mod = 0.0001 endif
! =============================================================================
iSashCutType = SASHCUT_NONE if not(lod3D = 1 | lod3D = 5) then ! Simple | Chinese if gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_FIXED_SCREW |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_SIDE_HUNG |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_SIDE_HUNG_M |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_TILT_TURN |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_TILT_TURN_M |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_BOTTOM_HUNG |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_TOP_HUNG |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_DOUBLE_SIDE_HUNG |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_DOUBLE_TILT_TURN |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_DOUBLE_TILT_TURN_M then iSashCutType = SASHCUT_REBATE if gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_SLIDING_HOR |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_SLIDING_HOR_M |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_DOUBLE_SLIDING_HOR |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_DOUBLE_SLIDING_HOR_M |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_SLIDING_VER |\ gs_optype_m_01 = SASH_DOUBLE_SLIDING_VER then iSashCutType = SASHCUT_MIDDLE endif
dyfw1 = gs_frame_width/cos(topAngle)+(a/2 - gs_frame_width)*tan(topAngle) dyfw2 = -gs_frame_width/cos(topAngle)+(a/2 - gs_frame_width)*tan(topAngle)
dysw1 = (gs_frame_width + simp_mod)/cos(topAngle)+(a/2 - gs_frame_width - simp_mod)*tan(topAngle) dysw2 = -(gs_frame_width + simp_mod)/cos(topAngle)+(a/2 - gs_frame_width - simp_mod)*tan(topAngle)
dyrw1 = (gs_frame_width - gs_rebate_width)/cos(topAngle)+(a/2 - gs_frame_width + gs_rebate_width)*tan(topAngle) dyrw2 = -(gs_frame_width - gs_rebate_width)/cos(topAngle)+(a/2 - gs_frame_width + gs_rebate_width)*tan(topAngle)
dy1 = -frame_toler/cos(topAngle)+(a/2 + rightOvhg)*tan(topAngle) dy2 = frame_toler/cos(topAngle)+(a/2 + leftOvhg)*tan(topAngle)
